      <div class="flow-step">
        <div class="step-num display-font">1</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Intake &amp; Scope Balancing</h3>
          <p>I operate intake loops structured on clean, decoupled milestones. I balance async leadership frameworks against actual resource availability to eliminate upfront scoping bottlenecks before production cycles commit hours.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <div class="step-num display-font">2</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Rigorous Execution &amp; Scale</h3>
          <p>I own the pipeline infrastructure that shapes abstract curriculum ideas into hardened, shipping programs. At PitchBook, I orchestrated a complex matrix delivery framework to accurately roll out intermediate curriculum paths across 600 separate team targets simultaneously.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-step">
        <div class="step-num display-font">3</div>
        <div>
          <h3>Transitioning to Self-Service</h3>
          <p>I actively replace fragile, high-touch training overhead with reliable self-service logic layers—deploying structures like 84 programmatic interactive system simulators to reduce downstream managerial instruction burdens by up to 50%.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: DATA & AI INFRASTRUCTURE -->
  <section id="data">
    <h2 class="display-font">3. Data Instrumentation &amp; AI Integration</h2>
    <div class="board-layout">
      <div class="block">
        <div class="block-tag">BI &amp; Tooling</div>
        <h3>Data Autonomy</h3>
        <p>I design my own tracking instrumentation matrices and write targeted queries directly inside deep BI architectures, bypassing engineering dependencies entirely.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Looker &amp; Tableau Dashboards:</strong> Created tracking logic architectures explicitly mapping education engagement patterns cleanly against real retention variables.</li>
          <li><strong>Rate of Task Usage:</strong> Co-designed a predictive user telemetry health engine to signal plan utilization thresholds long before churn windows opened.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="block">
        <div class="block-tag">AI Engineering</div>
        <h3>Automated AI Pipelines</h3>
        <p>I build programmatic automation directly into my daily operational fabrics using advanced LLM processing sequences.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Custom Claude Layers:</strong> Built automated engines parsing deep programmatic learner session data logs directly through custom-engineered Claude skills.</li>
          <li><strong>Automated Playbooks:</strong> Programmed logic pipelines converting text streams into structured, instantly actionable manager summary maps and automated data logs.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <h2 class="display-font" style="justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 20px; border: none;">Let's build the systems next.</h2>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 40px; font-size: 1.1rem; color: #555;">I engineer the foundational stacks that empower scale. Let's trace out a clear path together.</p>
    <a href="mailto:your.email@example.com" class="cta-btn display-font">Initialize Conversation</a>
    <p class="handwritten" style="margin-top: 40px; opacity: 0.6; font-size: 1.1rem;">— Hand-sketched logic for modern execution environments —</p>
  </footer>
</div>

</body>
</html>
